Ice Storm

Control of the weather provides much of a druid's
destructive power, and this spell demonstrates that.
With but a word, the druid conjures a hailstorm to
pelt everything in the area.  This spell is often
used against numbers of magic-resistant creatures,
since the hail is not itself magical; however, the
damage is not great, and heavily armored creatures
may escape unscathed.  You need not fear harming
another druid or their charmed or summoned creatures
with this spell.

Command: icestorm
Base Cost: 90 SP
Base Recovery: medium-long
Base Effect: damage (low, area)
Base Duration: instant
Guild Level: 9
